Membership Categories
Golfing Memberships
Stockholder Membership
$225/Month
$35/Month Food Minimum
The Stockholder Membership requires an upfront purchase of $250 worth of stock. This membership gives you 1 stockholders vote and the  opportunity to potentially serve on the Board of Directors.
Discounted prices, are available to all Stockholders, this membership includes the golf course, Jack's bar and grill, dining, the pool, and the tennis courts.
Anyone the age of 40 years or older must sign up as stockholders.
30's Membership
$175/Month
$35/Month Food Minimum
The 30's Membership gives members full access to the club. This membership includes the golf course, Jack's bar and grill, dining, the pool, and the tennis courts.
​
Anyone between the ages of 30 and 39 years old must sign up to this membership. You still have the option to join as a Stockholder.
​
It is mandatory that once you reach 40 you must purchase stock and upgrade your membership to the Stockholder Membership.
20's Membership
$125/Month
$35/Month Food Minimum
The 20's Membership gives members access to the golf course, Jack's bar and grill, dining, the pool, and the tennis courts.
​
Anyone between the ages of 20 and 29 years old must sign up for this membership. You still have the option to join as a Stockholder Membership.
​
It is mandatory that once you reach the age of 30 you upgrade to 30's Membership. Once you reach 40 years of age, you must upgrade to Stockholder Membership.
​
​

Social Membership
$105/Month
$35/Month Food Minimum
The Social Membership gives members access to The Clubhouse, Jack's bar and grill, dining, the tennis courts, and the pool. This membership does not include golf.
Dining Membership
$45/Month
$35/Month Food Minimum
The Dining Membership gives members access to The Clubhouse, Jack's bar and grill, dining. This membership does not include golf, the pool, or tennis.
